text: == Deaths == * January 4 – Elizabeth Ann Seton, American saint (b. 1774) * February 23 – John Keats, British poet (b. 1795) * March 13 – John Hunter, second Governor of New South Wales (b. 1737) * May 5 – Napoleon I of France (b. 1769) * May 19 – Camille Jordan, French politician (b. 1771) * September 10 – Johann Dominicus Fiorillo, German painter and art historian
